short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Removes the intrusive and often blatantly incorrect "AI" Overview from standard searches.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Features:

- Simple switch to toggle AI Overview blocking
- Legacy Mode: Forces all searches to Google's "Web" mode
- Now Trademark infringement free!
